title: I Got The Most Famous Voices To Record My Voicemail... And You Can Call It
description: In this video, Max Fosh gets some of the most famous voices to record his voicemail message, and then he gives out his phone number for viewers to call and hear the messages.
summary: Max Fosh enlists famous voices to record his voicemail message and shares his phone number with viewers.
payoff: The payoff comes when viewers get to hear the famous voices on Max's voicemail message, creating a funny and unexpected experience for those who call.
